title: You're Dating Out of Your League w/ Harry Jowsey
description:
Let’s talk about dating and why so many people are lost in the gap between what they’re getting and what they want out of love. To get up close and personal about it, Shan welcomes Harry Jowsey to the podcast, who you might recognize as the Australian heartthrob from the 2020 season of Netflix's "Too Hot to Handle". So how is it that a 6'5", successful, wealthy, gorgeous, and emotionally available man is having trouble finding "the one"? The answer surprised him, and may even surprise you too.

 

Follow Shan on Instagram: www.instagram.com/shanboody 

 

Get your copy of Shan's Book "The Game of Desire" on Amazon

 

Follow Harry Jowsey on Instagram: www.instagram.com/harryjowsey 

 

Listen to "Tap in with Harry Jowsey" wherever you are listening to this podcast

 

Follow Los on Instagram: www.instagram.com/blamelos 

 

Listen to Los and his 2 co-hosts every week on "Enjoy the Podcast" wherever you are listening to this podcast

 

Follow Chelsea on Instagram: www.instagram.com/chealseaprobably
